{{> header}}
<h1>{{newMemberName}} joined {{orgName}} 🎉</h1>
<p>Hi {{inviterName}}, great news — <strong>{{newMemberName}}</strong> (<a href="mailto:{{newMemberEmail}}">{{newMemberEmail}}</a>) has accepted your invitation and joined <strong>{{orgName}}</strong>.</p>
<p>They are now a member of your organization and can access boards and tasks you've shared with them.</p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin:28px 0;">
  <a href="{{orgUrl}}" class="btn">Go to {{orgName}}</a>
</p>
{{> footer}}
